(11, 1, '2023-09-05 11:11:59', '2023-09-05 14:11:59', '\n					<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"wide\",\"fontSize\":\"gigantic\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.1\"}}} -->\n					<h2 class=\"alignwide has-text-align-wide has-gigantic-font-size\" style=\"line-height:1.1\">Crie seu site com blocos</h2>\n					<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n					<!-- wp:spacer -->\n					<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n					<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n					<!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"align\":\"wide\",\"className\":\"is-style-twentytwentyone-columns-overlap\"} -->\n					<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide are-vertically-aligned-center is-style-twentytwentyone-columns-overlap\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n					<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\"><!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"full\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n					<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/themes/twentytwentyone/assets/images/roses-tremieres-hollyhocks-1884.jpg\" alt=\"&#8220;Roses Trémières&#8221; por Berthe Morisot\"/></figure>\n					<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n					<!-- wp:spacer -->\n					<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n					<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n					<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"full\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"is-style-twentytwentyone-image-frame\"} -->\n					<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-large is-style-twentytwentyone-image-frame\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/themes/twentytwentyone/assets/images/in-the-bois-de-boulogne.jpg\" alt=\"&#8220;No Bois de Boulogne&#8221; de Berthe Morisot\"/></figure>\n					<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n					<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n					<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n					<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\"><!-- wp:spacer -->\n					<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n					<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n					<!-- wp:image {\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"alignfull size-full is-style-twentytwentyone-border\"} -->\n					<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large alignfull size-full is-style-twentytwentyone-border\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/themes/twentytwentyone/assets/images/young-woman-in-mauve.jpg\" alt=\"&#8220;Jovem mulher em Mauve&#8221; de Berthe Morisot\"/></figure>\n					<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n					<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n					<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n					<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n					<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n					<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n					<!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"top\",\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n					<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide are-vertically-aligned-top\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"top\"} -->\n					<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n					<h3>Adicione padrões de blocos</h3>\n					<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n					<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n					<p>Os padrões de blocos são grupos de blocos pré-desenhados. Para adicionar um, selecione o botão Adicionar bloco [+] na barra de ferramentas na parte superior do editor. Mude para a aba &quot;Padrões&quot; embaixo da barra de busca e escolha um padrão.</p>\n					<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n					<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n					<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"top\"} -->\n					<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n					<h3>Molduras nas imagens</h3>\n					<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n					<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n					<p>Twenty Twenty-One inclui bordas elegantes para seu conteúdo. Com um bloco de imagem selecionado, abra o painel &quot;Estilos&quot; dentro da barra lateral do Editor. Selecione o estilo de bloco &quot;Moldura&quot; para ativá-lo.</p>\n					<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n					<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n					<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"top\"} -->\n					<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n					<h3>Sobrepor colunas</h3>\n					<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n					<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n					<p>Twenty Twenty-One também inclui um estilo de sobreposição para blocos de colunas. Com um bloco de colunas selecionado, abra o painel &quot;Estilos&quot; dentro da barra lateral do Editor. Escolha o estilo de bloco &quot;Sobrepor&quot; para experimentá-lo.</p>\n					<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n					<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n					<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n					<!-- wp:spacer -->\n					<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n					<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n					<!-- wp:cover {\"overlayColor\":\"green\",\"contentPosition\":\"center center\",\"align\":\"wide\",\"className\":\"is-style-twentytwentyone-border\"} -->\n					<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignwide has-green-background-color has-background-dim is-style-twentytwentyone-border\"><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n					<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n					<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n					<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"huge\"} -->\n					<p class=\"has-huge-font-size\">Precisa de ajuda?</p>\n					<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n					<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":75} -->\n					<div style=\"height:75px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n					<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n					<!-- wp:columns -->\n					<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n					<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n					<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/twenty-twenty-one/\">Ler a documentação do tema</a></p>\n					<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n					<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n					<!-- wp:column -->\n					<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n					<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/theme/twentytwentyone/\">Confira os fóruns de suporte</a></p>\n					<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n					<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n					<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n					<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n					<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n					<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>\n					<!-- /wp:cover -->', 'Crie seu site com blocos', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-09-05 11:11:59', '2023-09-05 14:11:59', '', 6, 'http://localhost/?p=11', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(12, 1, '2023-09-05 11:11:59', '2023-09-05 14:11:59', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Você pode ser um artista que queira se apresentar aqui, ou talvez queira descrever a missão da sua empresa.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Sobre', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-09-05 11:11:59', '2023-09-05 14:11:59', '', 7, 'http://localhost/?p=12', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(13, 1, '2023-09-05 11:11:59', '2023-09-05 14:11:59', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Esta é uma página com algumas informações básicas de contato, como um endereço e número de telefone. Você também pode experimentar usar um plugin para adicionar um formulário de contato.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Contato', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-09-05 11:11:59', '2023-09-05 14:11:59', '', 8, 'http://localhost/?p=13', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
